      "title": "Meemure stops at Dambade",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A 19-year-old married woman was killed and six others were injured when a bus carrying a group of people visiting the Meemure village in Wariyapola fell into a precipice in the Dambade area on the Hunnasgiriya-Meemure road.",
        "The injured have been admitted to Medamahanuwara and Teldeniya hospitals, Udadumbara Police said."
      ],
